title: Alaves vs Barcelona LIVE: Messi and Co look to close gap | Daily Mail Online
text: Alaves vs Barcelona LIVE: Lionel Messi and Co look to close the gap on Real Madrid in La Liga title race Barcelona are currently a point behind Real Madrid, but have played twice more Luis Enrique's side can go top - if only temporarily - with a victory over Alaves Alaves recorded a 2-1 win in the reverse fixture at the Nou Camp in September These two sides will meet again at the end of May in final of the Copa del Rey
